, <a href="/web/20180712201410/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SPN_CUI=C0182349&amp;fLockTerm=SYSTEM%2c+TOMOGRAPHY%2c+COMPUTED%2c+EMISSION">SYSTEM, TOMOGRAPHY, COMPUTED, EMISSION</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712201410/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SPN_CUI=C0936234&amp;fLockTerm=SYSTEM%2c+X-RAY%2c+TOMOGRAPHY%2c+COMPUTED">SYSTEM, X-RAY, TOMOGRAPHY, COMPUTED</a>
                    </div>
